{"tid":1368923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 我想講既係，其實IVE仔都有資格發聲架","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T09:11:52.000Z","uid":52658,"like":148,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fb1a5704502f97ebc8494e04c41318c2153fb976","tid":1368923,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5q5KAd9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5q5KAd9.png&h=f3a218c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地係一班就grad既i大仔 <br />\n雖然我地唔係社會既菁英<br />\n讀書無人咁叻<br />\n但我地有一顆熱愛香港既心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然而家暫時得三張<br />\n但我相信好多ive既同學 同我地有一樣既目標<br />\n黎緊我地會係學校宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將會有更多人一齊放低學生證走出黎為香港發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多 7.27元朗見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f4baf0bd8079f2ac890f5b05b044897e569691","tid":1368923,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"61d827cd1a18208a44aec1f06f04a33f461d29ff","tid":1368923,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb56578d8ef51cec6a6e70236dce3ef1474c0b1","tid":1368923,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca754e4a85f7b00fb73e0d79e4ab38a7a5b846f","tid":1368923,"uid":150361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pi